268
00:24:57,870 --> 00:24:59,530
No.

269
00:24:59,530 --> 00:25:01,720
-A long spear?
-No.

270
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:04,120
How about flying darts?

271
00:25:13,090 --> 00:25:16,000
This is an insult from Chu Xiuming on my ability!

272
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:18,580
It's an insult to my character!

273
00:25:20,330 --> 00:25:22,410
The skills I learnt with Susu,

274
00:25:22,410 --> 00:25:24,990
why aren't any of them useful?

275
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:44,450
Thankfully, Rou Rou was prepared and gave me osmanthus candy!

276
00:25:44,450 --> 00:25:46,540
Or else, drinking this tasteless congee every day,

277
00:25:46,540 --> 00:25:48,880
I'll die!

278
00:25:58,410 --> 00:26:00,690
Yummy!

279
00:26:01,570 --> 00:26:03,220
What are you doing?

280
00:26:04,100 --> 00:26:05,370
I-!

281
00:26:05,370 --> 00:26:06,940
Chu Xiuming, you did that on purpose!

282
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:09,700
