283
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:11,970
There's something wrong with this congee.

284
00:26:11,970 --> 00:26:14,450
Is there arsenic or poison?

285
00:26:14,450 --> 00:26:17,210
I think there's something wrong with <i>you</i>!

286
00:26:17,210 --> 00:26:20,850
If you want to eat, just get another bowl.

287
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:23,480
Forget it!

288
00:26:30,910 --> 00:26:34,070
Even the kitchen staff must be carefully investigated.

289
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:35,640
I understand.

290
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:44,780
<i>New soldiers are taking a bath! Everyone come together! Dont' be late!</i>

291
00:26:56,770 --> 00:26:59,360
Even bath times are pre-set in the military.

292
00:26:59,360 --> 00:27:01,220
There's so many soldiers taking a bath together.

293
00:27:01,220 --> 00:27:03,680
I won't have a chance!

294
00:27:06,370 --> 00:27:07,930
If I stand here without moving,

295
00:27:07,930 --> 00:27:10,060
I won't break a sweat.

296
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:14,740
Why don't I return to the manor to bathe?

297
00:27:16,520 --> 00:27:18,780
It's not that close.

298
00:27:18,780 --> 00:27:22,410
I can't go back and forth every day.

299
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:42,250
You want to go to the bathhouse?

300
00:27:42,250 --> 00:27:45,610
Um...I...I was taking a walk after dinner.

301
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:48,850
This is for washing my face!

302
00:27:48,850 --> 00:27:51,860
My face is all dirty after a day of practice.

303
00:27:52,780 --> 00:27:55,850
If you want to take a bath, you can go to my tent.

304
00:27:55,850 --> 00:27:59,030
Why?  Go to your tent?

305
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:00,780
Didn't you divorce me?

306
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:03,610
Even if I'm covered in dirt I won't go to your tent to bathe!

307
00:28:06,420 --> 00:28:09,890
Chu Xiuming. You won't give me a weapon, and you won't let me eat.

308
00:28:09,890 --> 00:28:11,730
Now I can't even take a bath!

309
00:28:11,730 --> 00:28:13,240
You're not only torturing me in food and drink,

310
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:16,520
you also want to take advantage of me? In your dreams!

311
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,910
You're done?

312
00:28:37,490 --> 00:28:39,100
Come, come.

313
00:28:39,620 --> 00:28:41,190
My lady.

314
00:28:41,190 --> 00:28:44,130
Bao Zitou! Where are my blankets?

315
00:28:44,130 --> 00:28:45,600
Your blankets have been arranged.

316
00:28:45,600 --> 00:28:48,190
I will take you there right now.

317
00:28:55,270 --> 00:28:59,230
Bao Zitou! This is the General's tent!

318
00:28:59,230 --> 00:29:01,020
He wants me to spend the night here?

319
00:29:01,020 --> 00:29:02,970
Yes, my lady.

320
00:29:05,810 --> 00:29:07,460
Then go tell the General!

321
00:29:07,460 --> 00:29:09,250
I voluntarily entered the military!

322
00:29:09,250 --> 00:29:12,170
So I should receive the same treatment as the other soldiers!

323
00:29:12,170 --> 00:29:14,400
Besides, why didn't he come discuss this with  me,

324
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:16,390
and instead decided it for me?

325
00:29:16,390 --> 00:29:17,950
I'm not going!

326
00:29:17,950 --> 00:29:19,810
Also, General should know this very well!

327
00:29:19,810 --> 00:29:22,070
I have no right to enter his tent!

328
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:26,540
My lady, please stop fighting with the General.

329
00:29:26,540 --> 00:29:28,470
Take me to the new soldier tent right now!

330
00:29:28,470 --> 00:29:31,160
I'm tired, I want to rest!

331
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:33,090
Please!

332
00:29:39,210 --> 00:29:41,790
General, this...

333
00:29:45,650 --> 00:29:47,220
If she wants to live there,

334
00:29:47,220 --> 00:29:49,550
then make arrangements for her.

335
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:51,340
The soldiers won't dare to make a fuss.

336
00:29:51,340 --> 00:29:52,850
Yes!

337
00:30:02,380 --> 00:30:03,450
<i>Come help me fold this.</i>

338
00:30:03,450 --> 00:30:04,830
Okay.

339
00:30:06,590 --> 00:30:08,060
So tired, let's sleep.

340
00:30:08,060 --> 00:30:09,760
It's been a long day.

341
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:12,200
Aiya...

342
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:16,370
Everyone! Where should I sleep?

343
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:26,130
Why don't I sleep outside?

344
00:30:27,710 --> 00:30:29,260
Hey! Wait!

345
00:30:29,260 --> 00:30:31,310
Come back, come back!

346
00:30:31,310 --> 00:30:33,950
That's not what I meant!

347
00:30:36,990 --> 00:30:39,060
Bao Zitou, they all-!

348
00:30:39,060 --> 00:30:40,120
It's fine!

349
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:43,050
No! There's still practice tomorrow! This is not right!

350
00:30:43,050 --> 00:30:45,480
Um...is there any other place to sleep?

351
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:48,440
Don't worry, my lady. The soldiers are all rough people.

352
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:51,030
They usually sleep outside during practice.

353
00:30:51,030 --> 00:30:53,680
Just rest here.

354
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:55,190
I-!

355
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:39,290
This won't do!

356
00:31:39,810 --> 00:31:42,130
When they're soldiers, they die on the battlefield!

357
00:31:42,130 --> 00:31:45,120
When I'm a soldier, I'm going to itch to death in the camp!

358
00:31:45,740 --> 00:31:48,080
This is too embarrassing!

359
00:31:51,290 --> 00:31:55,240
It's so late already. Everyone should be asleep, right?

360
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:57,830
Then no one will discover me, right?

361
00:32:33,060 --> 00:32:34,950
Stop right there! Who is it?

362
00:32:36,670 --> 00:32:39,920
Come out! If you don't, we'll have to go in.

363
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,510
What's going on?

364
00:32:47,490 --> 00:32:49,250
- Your Ladyship? 
 - Your Ladyship?

365
00:33:08,180 --> 00:33:10,630
General, Her Ladyship has arrived.

366
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:20,980
You've gone through a lot of hardships these past couple of days.

367
00:33:22,290 --> 00:33:25,210
Some tea from the manor has been brought here. Please have some.

368
00:33:26,290 --> 00:33:28,410
General, just be frank with me.

369
00:33:28,410 --> 00:33:32,320
Since I've violated martial law, you should simply accord me the punishment befitting of the crime.

370
00:33:36,950 --> 00:33:39,110
This subordinate of yours will take his leave.

371
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:52,000
If you refuse to return to the manor, you'll have to sleep in my tent every night

372
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:54,370
and you'll have to bathe here as well.

373
00:33:55,330 --> 00:33:58,900
Since you've given me the divorce letter, I'm no longer your wife.

374
00:33:58,900 --> 00:34:01,100
Why should you be so concerned about me?

375
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:03,320
General, what do you mean by this?

376
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:06,230
Every single person here is male.

377
00:34:06,230 --> 00:34:08,370
It would be very inconvenient for you to sleep and bathe here.

378
00:34:08,370 --> 00:34:11,700
Moreover, everyone in the army knows you're a girl. How're you going to live together with them?

379
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:13,720
I have to stay here just because you tell me to?

380
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:15,720
You absolutely must stay here!

381
00:34:19,350 --> 00:34:21,720
There is only one room here. How am I supposed to stay here?

382
00:34:21,720 --> 00:34:23,440
I'll have another bed made and sleep there.

383
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:26,330
We will sleep in the same room and not bother each other.

384
00:34:27,170 --> 00:34:31,070
Chu Xiuming, you're saying the same thing you said back in the manor.

385
00:34:31,070 --> 00:34:34,320
You've swept everything under the carpet so cleanly.

386
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:37,790
I, Shen Jin volunteered to join the army. I have my own plans.

387
00:34:37,790 --> 00:34:39,830
You don't have to worry about me.

388
00:34:46,790 --> 00:34:50,310
I'll agree to any demands you make,

389
00:34:50,310 --> 00:34:52,730
as long as you don't cause trouble within the army and stay here obediently.

390
00:34:55,070 --> 00:34:58,860
You'll give me... whatever I want?

391
00:35:02,470 --> 00:35:06,080
A true gentleman never goes back on his words.

392
00:35:06,080 --> 00:35:08,030
All right, General.

393
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:11,030
I didn't sleep well at all last night and I'm extremely tired.

394
00:35:11,030 --> 00:35:13,080
I want to drink some wine and relax a little.

395
00:35:13,080 --> 00:35:15,950
You know that wine is prohibited within the army, so by making such a request, you're obviously–

396
00:35:15,950 --> 00:35:18,770
Seeing as I'm only a little girl,  how would I know that wine is prohibited within the army?

397
00:35:18,770 --> 00:35:22,500
You were the one who wanted to meet my needs. All I want is some wine.

398
00:35:22,500 --> 00:35:26,590
You're a formidable and great General, how could you not have any wine with you?

399
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:33,030
Fine.

400
00:35:33,890 --> 00:35:38,180
If I give you wine, does that mean you'll agree to my request?

401
00:35:38,180 --> 00:35:41,540
I'll agree to your request as long as you give me wine.

402
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:50,980
"How many times can I laugh heartily throughout my life,"

403
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:54,070
"I have to drink 'til I'm drunk since I'm drinking with such great friends." (T/N quoting poetry from Tang dynasty)

404
00:35:54,070 --> 00:35:55,730
I feel so carefree.

405
00:35:55,730 --> 00:35:57,580
I have beautiful scenery to admire

406
00:35:57,580 --> 00:36:00,090
and I also have wine to drink.

407
00:36:01,420 --> 00:36:04,350
General, you're still the one who has been thoughtful.

408
00:36:04,350 --> 00:36:06,680
I just knew you had wine with you.

409
00:36:06,680 --> 00:36:10,220
But that means you have violated martial law.

410
00:36:10,830 --> 00:36:15,030
If I'd let you drink on camp grounds, who knows how much trouble you would've caused.

411
00:36:15,030 --> 00:36:20,700
Chu Xiuming, do you really think I'm one of your subordinate troops?

412
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:26,770
Let me tell you this. I'm your wife whom the Emperor has bestowed upon... You...

413
00:36:28,740 --> 00:36:32,050
Let me offer you some advice.

414
00:36:32,050 --> 00:36:36,170
You believe you're so infallible, don't you know?

415
00:36:36,170 --> 00:36:38,390
You have the worst temper

416
00:36:38,390 --> 00:36:41,100
and you walk around all day with that serious look on your face.

417
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:45,030
I can't spot a single bit of humaneness in you.

418
00:36:49,060 --> 00:36:52,210
What are you doing? Haven't you already divorced me?

419
00:36:52,210 --> 00:36:55,510
Don't touch me.

420
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:59,650
People say, "Women's hearts are just like a needle at the bottom of the sea." (T/N Chinese proverb: women's minds are hard to understand.)

421
00:36:59,650 --> 00:37:02,180
You're a grown man,

422
00:37:02,180 --> 00:37:05,030
yet you're cold one minute and hot the next.

423
00:37:05,030 --> 00:37:08,420
I protected the manor for you.

424
00:37:08,420 --> 00:37:11,070
I came to the army camp because of you.

425
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:15,760
I've done so much for you,

426
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:21,000
yet you not only wish to divorce me, but you also wish to chase me away from you.

427
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:28,400
You used to call me "my Lady" all the time,

428
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:31,360
but now you don't even want to look at me.

429
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:35,960
I don't mean anything to you anymore.

430
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:39,060
I dare you to call me "my Lady" again.

431
00:37:39,060 --> 00:37:41,680
Look! You just won't do it.

432
00:37:41,680 --> 00:37:45,480
Look at how heartless you are!

433
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:02,690
There's a lake here!

434
00:38:03,730 --> 00:38:08,460
Thank the spirits of the sky and land. I can finally take a bath.

435
00:38:12,260 --> 00:38:14,770
There's a lake in front of you! Be careful!

436
00:38:15,950 --> 00:38:17,460
My Lady!

437
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:22,100
My Lady!

438
00:38:25,090 --> 00:38:26,660
My Lady.

439
00:38:37,970 --> 00:38:40,050
