440
00:38:40,050 --> 00:38:42,200
Get out of the lake and put your cloths on quickly.

441
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:44,700
Look at these strange things you're saying.

442
00:38:44,700 --> 00:38:47,920
How am I supposed to take a bath if I don't take off my clothes?

443
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:52,890
Heaven must be truly on my side. There's actually a lake here for me to bathe in!

444
00:38:53,610 --> 00:38:57,010
Chu Xiuming, did you just call me "my Lady"?

445
00:38:57,010 --> 00:38:59,140
Did you?

446
00:38:59,140 --> 00:39:01,710
I was under a state of duress just now, so I accidentally blurted it out.

447
00:39:01,710 --> 00:39:03,670
I will never call you that again.

448
00:39:04,200 --> 00:39:06,290
Fine, don't then.

449
00:39:06,290 --> 00:39:09,000
But why have you turned your back towards me?

450
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:11,850
Do you want to turn around and take a bath with me?

451
00:39:11,850 --> 00:39:14,780
If you wish to take a bath, do so and then quickly put your clothes back on.

452
00:39:14,780 --> 00:39:16,810
I will wait for you up there.

453
00:39:18,460 --> 00:39:22,790
We're in the middle of the wilderness, and it's just the two of us here.

454
00:39:22,790 --> 00:39:26,420
And... I've got so little on.

455
00:39:26,420 --> 00:39:28,780
Do you dare turn around to look at me?

456
00:39:29,780 --> 00:39:31,810
Stop being mischievous.

457
00:39:31,810 --> 00:39:33,530
I'm not being mischievous!

458
00:39:33,530 --> 00:39:37,200
Are you even a man? Do you dare turn around and face me?

459
00:39:37,200 --> 00:39:40,650
It's not safe wading in unknown waters while drunk. Aren't you going to quickly come up?

460
00:39:40,650 --> 00:39:46,330
Chu Xiuming! I am your wife who you legally and legitimately married!

461
00:39:46,330 --> 00:39:48,410
Not only are you divorcing me,

462
00:39:48,410 --> 00:39:51,460
