463
00:39:51,460 --> 00:39:55,990
I'm telling you, if you won't turn around today, then I'm never coming up to the shore!

464
00:39:56,640 --> 00:39:59,520
If you're still angry because of the divorce letter,

465
00:39:59,520 --> 00:40:01,030
