466
00:40:01,030 --> 00:40:03,680
But you must get out immediately, and put your cloths back on!

467
00:40:03,680 --> 00:40:07,250
It's not safe wading in unknown waters while drunk. What if–

468
00:40:09,660 --> 00:40:11,260
My Lady!

